add "hookName" option to installable hook config

- set "hookName" in order to specify installable hook name.
e.g. {
  "sails": {
    "isHook": true,
    "hookName": "myHook"
  }
}

updating things that are done in v0.11

socket.io 1.0 is live in sails@0.11.x

